---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="BridgeAIChat Downloads" description="Install BridgeAIChat app and agent releases.">
  <section class="surface">
    <div class="eyebrow">Downloads</div>
    <h1>Install from GitHub Releases.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      The beta ships as two release archives: the app repo for the gateway and hosted UI, and the agent repo for
      remote device runtimes.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap grid two">
    <div class="card stack">
      <div class="eyebrow">bridge-ai-app</div>
      <h2>Gateway + hosted UI</h2>
      <p>Download the latest app release, extract it, and run the bundled gateway launcher.</p>
      <p><a href="https://github.com/akshaymemane/bridge-ai-app/releases">Browse app releases</a></p>
      <div class="note"><strong>Includes:</strong> <code>bridge-gateway</code>, built UI, <code>install-app.sh</code>, and <code>SHA256SUMS.txt</code>.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card stack">
      <div class="eyebrow">bridge-ai-agent</div>
      <h2>Remote device runtime</h2>
      <p>Download the matching agent release, extract it on the remote machine, and run <code>bash install-agent.sh</code>.</p>
      <p><a href="https://github.com/akshaymemane/bridge-ai-agent/releases">Browse agent releases</a></p>
      <div class="note"><strong>Includes:</strong> <code>bridge-agent</code>, <code>agent.yaml.example</code>, <code>install-agent.sh</code>, and <code>SHA256SUMS.txt</code>.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Compatibility</div>
      <h2>Version matrix</h2>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>App</th>
              <th>Agent</th>
              <th>Tested setups</th>
              <th>Notes</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>v0.1.0-beta.1</td>
              <td>v0.1.0-beta.1</td>
              <td>macOS host + macOS agent, macOS host + Raspberry Pi agent, macOS host + Linux VPS agent</td>
              <td>Tailnet-input beta flow with Tailscale API-backed device discovery.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
